description: Raves are the best parties, specially if they are full of glow sticks, black lights and cocks. This is exactly what this latest submission is all about. After partying in the dorm for a while, a girl notice that three of the dudes were missing. They decided to look for them and found them in the bathroom blowing each other up. Once they got back to the dorm, it was on, all night long. The party turned quickly from glow sticks to glow dicks, and everybody was loving it.
title: Glow Dicks
